    ) -> tuple[npt.NDArray, npt.NDArray]:
    """Compute the intersecting pairs of triangles in a surface mesh.

    Parameters
    ----------
    vertices : npt.ArrayLike

    faces : npt.ArrayLike

    Returns
    -------
